race.description: Two Rivers Wines Country Boosted Handicap (Bm66)
race.comment: DAWN COUNTY (1) was a comfortable winner over the mile at Narromine last start, bringing up his second success from four runs this prep. Well placed again and with the claim keeping him in light, he looks hard to hold out. HIBIKI HARMONY (7) chased that runner gamely last time and now meets him 2kgs better at the weights. Back to a trip she's unbeaten at and reunited with Bell, she shapes as a genuine threat. SMART JAZZ (4) put it all together with a strong Taree win last time. This is tougher but a repeat of that effort sees him right in the mix. CAPICELLA (6) resumes on the fresh side and maps for a soft run from the inside draw. Her form measures up and she'll give a bold sight. THE IMPECKABLE (5) has been below best lately but a quick turnaround could spark improvement.
